    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你准备好来玩一款既可爱又具有挑战性的找物游戏了吗？进入《100 Hidden Capybaras》——终极找物冒险，在这里你的任务是找到并收集100只可爱的水豚，每只都藏在精美设计的场景中！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3288020/extras/503eb4917e7029e265a0edb03289a945.poster.avif?t=1752568319\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3288020/extras/503eb4917e7029e265a0edb03289a945.webm?t=1752568319\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🌿 探索充满茂密森林、迷人村庄、秘密地牢和未知星球的惊艳环境。🏘🐉🪐</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3288020/extras/67b9714845aeef907f7fedb0d6dd7f49.poster.avif?t=1752568319\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3288020/extras/67b9714845aeef907f7fedb0d6dd7f49.webm?t=1752568319\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >发现我们毛茸茸的小伙伴们所有的藏身之处，同时测试你的观察技巧。🔍</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3288020/extras/bcf20d444847ae7696f307c1cb107de1.poster.avif?t=1752568319\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3288020/extras/bcf20d444847ae7696f307c1cb107de1.webm?t=1752568319\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >享受生动的画面和令人愉悦的配乐，让你在整个旅程中保持投入。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3288020/extras/0ec8dc2ee7d53523831fa52029104659.poster.avif?t=1752568319\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3288020/extras/0ec8dc2ee7d53523831fa52029104659.webm?t=1752568319\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >今天就将《100 Hidden Capybaras》加入你的愿望清单吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3288020/extras/73abf08ce8fd79bc5c786a3af96f497b.poster.avif?t=1752568319\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3288020/extras/73abf08ce8fd79bc5c786a3af96f497b.webm?t=1752568319\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p>",
